  <meta content="Like the map on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/PittsburghLentenFishFryMap

Lent begins on February 18, 2015.

Gray markers = need 2015 info
Blue = church
Red = fire department
Green = community org.
Yellow = business
Star = lunch AND dinner hours
Round pin = dinner hours only
Pierogie = mentions &quot;homemade pierogies&quot;

If you would like to have your fish fry added  to this map, please email me the information at hollenbarmer@gmail.com.  

Important: Verify prices and location before you visit a fish fry on this map. I've tried to get everything right, but mistakes happen sometimes!
